high_descs: Walk ahead to the counter, then turn right to face the stove.
Take the plate out of the cabinet above the stove.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the plate in fridge on the top shelf, right in the center. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Place the plate on the table, in the front right corner.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled plate on a table.

high_descs: Walk up to the counter, then turn right and walk over to the oven and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the upper cabinet and take the plate out of the cabinet, then close the cabinet.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the plate inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and take out the now chilled plate, then close the fridge.
Turn right and walk towards the door, the hang a right and walk forward and turn around to face the white table.
Put the chilled grey plate on the front right corner of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled grey plate on a white table.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the stove and look up at the cabinet above the stove.
Pick up the plate in the cabinet.
Turn to the right and go to the fridge.
Put the plate in the middle of top shelf in the fridge, close the fridge, open the fridge and pick the plate back up.
Turn right and go to the white table with shelves.
Put the plate in the right of the apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate on the white table with shelves.
